      "message": "I think of this as giving boost some flexibility in choosing it\u0027s kernel interface for specific use cases.  Otherwise why wouldn\u0027t they just have one feature flag?  I can\u0027t imagine why using io_uring over epoll for non-file IO would have any meaningful performance impact, but that\u0027s just my intution.  +1 since I can\u0027t see any down-side to using epoll for non-file IO.",
